ActGwich'in Land Claim Settlement Act
PrecisOrder approving an amendment to the GWICH'IN COMPREHENSIVE LAND CLAIM AGREEMENT which would provide a settlement corporation of the Gwich'in Tribal Council with the ability to provide distribution of capital to each Gwich'in participant in the 25 years from the date of settlement legislation, to a maximum cumulative amount per participant.
